==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Ђ''', '''ђ''' (''italics: Ђ, ђ'')

#The sixth letter of the Serbian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is '''ђ''' (đ) and it has the sound of English soft '''j''' in '''''J'''ack''. It is preceded by [[д|Д]] and followed by [[е|Е]].

